# wurst180: WURST inversion pulse
# ultra-wide band, low amplitude, adiabatic inversion pulse
# E. Kupce & R.Freeman, J.Magn.Reson., 115A, 273, (1995).
%
#       Shape Parameters
#       ----------------
amf 	= wr	(amplitude modulation function)
fmf 	= ls	(frequency modulation function)
fla 	= 180.0	(default flipangle on resonance)
pwbw 	= 80.0	(pulsewidth to bandwidth product)
adb     = 4.0   (adiabaticity on resonance)
c1      = 40.0  (power index, n)
steps 	= 200	(default number of steps)

